Mark your calendar for Google Cloud Next





Discover the next big thing in AI and cloud innovation. No matter what you want to do next, explore how to get started with new tools, live learning sessions, and demos. Join us in Las Vegas April 9-11, 2025.










Register now




























































Introducing Veo and Imagen 3 on Vertex AI





New image and video generation models are on Vertex AI. Veo is our most capable video generation model yet, creating high-quality videos from text or image prompts. Imagen 3 generates the most realistic and highest quality images from text prompts.















Learn more






































New in IDX: Interactive Chat





Interactive Chat is the next chapter of AI assistance in Project IDX.




Turn conversational prompts into real actions integrated into an IDX workspace. Now available to all IDX users in preview.















Learn more





























Product updates














🐞Android Studio Ladybug feature drop is stable




Build high-quality Android apps, faster. The latest updates and new features are designed to accelerate your productivity with Gemini in Android Studio. Download the latest stable version today.















Learn more




















Get The Latest from Google Play




In 2024, Google Play became more than a store. In The Latest, get your recap of the new options, rewards, and content connecting your users to experiences they’ll love.















Read more




















Scale your Vertex AI RAG pipeline with confidence




Vertex AI RAG Engine connects LLMs to real-time, accurate data sources to help build grounded gen AI applications. It simplifies integration, reduces ambiguity and offers flexibility with customizable solutions.















Learn more




















Just for devs, the Chrome roundup




Build more imaginative web experiences with less lift. Discover how Chrome is re-imagining the web with AI in DevTools, built-in Gemini, and new UI capabilities.















Learn more





























Learning articles














Beyond the Basics: Get real-world gen AI skills




Open career doors and unlock your full earning potential with the latest gen AI courses on Google Cloud Skills Boost. Join the Innovators program and get 35 free credits toward 4 new learning paths.






















Learn more


































Integrate user messaging into your Android app




Learn how to communicate with users and build business with Firebase Cloud and In-App Messaging.






















Learn more


































Error correction with Google Quantum AI




Dig deep into quantum error correction. Includes an overview of quantum computing, quantum states and circuits, formalism of stabilizers, and Stim and Crumble software tools.






















Enroll now


































Implement recurring transactions with Google Pay




Ensure smooth and efficient integrations for your payment system. This comprehensive guide walks you through the implementation process and covers how merchant-initiated transactions work.






















Watch now




































Developer community














Meet the winners of the Chrome Built-in AI Challenge




8,600 participants. 650 complete submissions. 5 criteria: functionality, purpose, content, user experience, and technical execution. Only 6 winners.















Learn more




















Nonprofits: Gen AI Accelerator open call




Is your nonprofit or social enterprise looking to harness gen AI for social impact? You may be the right fit for the Google.org Accelerator. Apply to receive training and funding.















Learn more




















Google Cloud x MLB AI Hackathon




Use real data from Major League Baseball™ to showcase your AI skills and craft impactful applications. Registration open to all developers globally. Closes Feb 4, 2025.















Learn more


































