                 Hi Himanshi —  
                 &nbsp; 
                  We're thrilled to announce improvements to our core email verifier, used for both Email Finder and Email Verifier. 
                  
                 
                   &nbsp; 
                  
                  Here's what's new: 
                  
                  &nbsp; 
                  
                  Enhanced Accuracy:&nbsp;The verifier is now more precise and less error-prone. 
                  
                 
                   &nbsp; 
                  
                  Key Benefits: 
                  
                 
                   &nbsp; 
                  
                  
                  80%&nbsp;Reduction in business emails with unknown verification status.&nbsp;&nbsp; 
                  &nbsp;50%&nbsp;Increase** in business emails marked with a valid status. 
                  
                 
                   &nbsp; 
                  
                  These updates are already live, meaning you'll experience:&nbsp; 
                  
                  &nbsp;✅ More accurate email results&nbsp; 
                  
                  &nbsp;✅ Significantly lower bounce rates 
                  
                 
                   &nbsp; 
                  
                  Simplify Your Workflow&nbsp; 
                  
